column3: All you need is a Â£140 jersey from us to have fun
I can't get over the fact that someone at Rapha watched this in a conference room with some other higher ups and they said "This is great, let's post it"
What the hell is this Rapha? I love Rapha...I'm an RCC founding member...but this makes no sense to me.
I'm afraid Rapha has gotten to popular for their own good, like when someone gets famous then goes off the deep end.
Earings are ropes for sailing.Earrings are accessories for ears.These videos are consistently terrible. RIP the Rapha I used to love and relate to.
